name: Nature vs FBI
description:
A game made in 3 hours by Banan for Trijam #158

Everything was made in the 3 hours exept music and art.

You are a powerfull wizard with the power of nature. You are so powerfull that the FBI has decided to execute you.

Fight of waves of the FBI with your nature powers
